{
  "stem": "14251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as he saw things shaping up, he had that attic unit built at his own place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The trick was to do it without the knowledge of tenants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had over there in most buildings what was called a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH] was a person who served mostly as your handyman person, not the person who is the manager as far as renting and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, no, no-- only the physical aspects of the building and repairs and such.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, by this time, he had completed the-- the building was, I think, upstairs completed, my mother said, maybe four years before, so say, in '39.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because he had information, because he was a man who was well connected with data and had, for instance, the non-Jewish lawyer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He got a lot of information.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had that built.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Had one toilet, a small kitchen with a table and chairs for two, and everything in miniature.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you the square footage, but I would imagine something smaller than Anne Frank and family had from what I had seen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Much smaller.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was one window that was covered with tar paper so that no light would come out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was done up with electricity, the whole works.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Aside from that, the Levents had two postal carrier uniforms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Think of our mailman today in some blue outfit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They had two uniforms that would fit them, and they had-- felt that if they needed to escape-- if it came to hiding in there and escape, they would put these on and go over the roofs.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know what they pictured at age 70, but it was still a feeling of hope.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said to us, well, we don't know what you will do.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
